title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 13 2021

description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2: Alex Berenson joins Clay and Buck to give data analysis on covid vaccinations. Why are U.K. and Israel getting different results? Big Tech censorship is a threat to free speech everywhere. Kabul, the capital of Afghanistan, could fall to the Taliban in days. Everything that Biden touches, turns to the opposite of gold.
